.DT
query_save_file
Disk World creator help
query_save_file

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_save_file -  This function can be used to query what save file is in use for the suggestion box.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string query_save_file()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the full path to the file where the suggestions are kept.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/misc/suggestion_box.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function can be used to query what save file is in use for the
suggestion box.  Either a save file *or* a save directory is required.
or your suggestions will not save.  If both are set then the save file
will be used.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_save_dir() 

.EP

